title: 615. 10 Takeaways from Week 11
itunes:title: 615. 10 Takeaways from Week 11
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and pick ten storylines that stood out from Week 11 of the NFL season. To start off, the guys discuss Chiefs QB Patrick Mahomes being magnificent in his comeback against the Raiders (:57). Next, the trio look at how the Titans bullied the Ravens (4:20). Later, the guys debate if the Dolphins made the right decision benching QB Tua Tagovailoa vs. the Broncos (15:44). To wrap up the show, DJ, Bucky and Rhett talk about Chargers WR Keenan Allen being a zone buster after his huge performance against the Jets (41:28). All that and more in this packed episode.
